{% extends "layout.html.jinja" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">&gt; DOCS // COME FUNZIONA</h1>
    <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-outline-variant border-dashed border-t"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-6 font-mono text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      <span class="text-primary-container">OSSERVATORIO_SEO</span> &egrave; un hub giornaliero di news <em>SEO</em> e <em>AI</em>
      aggiornato automaticamente ogni mattina alle <span class="text-white">07:00 Europe/Rome</span>. Una pipeline
      automatizzata legge un insieme di fonti autorevoli, filtra le notizie fresche (ultime 24&nbsp;h), le riassume in italiano
      tramite AI e pubblica il risultato come sito statico.
    </p>
    <p>
      Ogni riassunto linka sempre alla fonte originale. I contenuti sono generati da AI e non rivisti editorialmente &mdash;
      per decisioni operative, consulta sempre la fonte.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">&gt; LE PAGINE</h2>
    <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-outline-variant border-dashed border-t"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-sm">
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ TODAY ] <code>/</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">La home. Mostra il feed del giorno: <span class="text-white">Top 10</span> numerato e tutte le notizie raggruppate in <span class="text-white">categorie</span>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ TOP WEEK ] <code>/top-settimana/</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Le 10 notizie pi&ugrave; importanti degli ultimi 7 giorni, finestra scorrevole aggiornata ogni giorno.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ TRACKER ] <code>/tracker/</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Dashboard settimanale sullo stato della ricerca in Italia: popolarit&agrave; delle AI (Google Trends), traffico bot, crawler AI, confronto Italia vs Mondo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ ARCHIVIO ] <code>/archivio/</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Indice cronologico per anno/mese/giorno. Ogni snapshot &egrave; un set disgiunto di notizie (solo 24&nbsp;h &rarr; zero duplicati).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ ARTICOLO ] <code>/archivio/AAAA/MM/GG/slug/</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Pagina dedicata per le notizie con importanza &ge; 4. Include JSON-LD NewsArticle per Google Discover.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-l-2 border-primary-container">
      <div class="text-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">[ FEED ] <code>/feed.xml</code></div>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Feed Atom per reader tradizionali come Feedly o Inoreader.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">&gt; FONTI MONITORATE</h2>
    <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-outline-variant border-dashed border-t"></div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-[10px] text-outline uppercase font-mono mb-6">{{ sources | length }} FONTI ATTIVE</p>
  {% for type_label, type_sources in sources_by_type.items() %}
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h3 class="text-primary-container font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3 pb-1 border-b border-outline-variant">[ {{ type_label }} // {{ type_sources | length }} ]</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
    {% for s in type_sources %}
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest font-mono text-xs">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-[#f5a623]">{{ '★' * s.authority }}</span>
        <span class="text-white">{{ s.name }}</span>
        <span class="text-outline text-[10px] uppercase">{{ s.id }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] uppercase">
        <span class="text-outline">{{ s.fetcher }}</span>
        <a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-outline hover:text-primary-container">{{ s.hostname }} &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">&gt; DOC WATCHER // PAGINE SORVEGLIATE</h2>
    <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-outline-variant border-dashed border-t"></div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-mono mb-6">
    Queste pagine vengono controllate ad ogni aggiornamento e confrontate con la versione precedente. Se il testo cambia in modo
    significativo, viene generato un item speciale nel feed con badge &#x26A0; e un diff leggibile.
  </p>
  <p class="text-[10px] text-outline uppercase font-mono mb-6">{{ doc_watcher_pages | length }} PAGINE SORVEGLIATE</p>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
  {% for p in doc_watcher_pages %}
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest font-mono text-xs">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <span class="text-[#f5a623]">{{ '★' * p.importance }}</span>
      <span class="text-white">{{ p.name }}</span>
      <span class="text-outline text-[10px] uppercase">[{{ p.type }}]</span>
    </div>
    <a href="{{ p.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-outline hover:text-primary-container text-[10px] uppercase">{{ p.hostname }} &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">&gt; RANKING &amp; CATEGORIE</h2>
    <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-outline-variant border-dashed border-t"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-6 font-mono text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
    <p>Ogni notizia riceve un punteggio basato su importanza (valutata dall'AI), autorevolezza della fonte, freschezza e tipo di contenuto. Le notizie con punteggio pi&ugrave; alto entrano nella <span class="text-white">Top 10</span>.</p>
    <p>Le 8 categorie sono: <span class="text-primary-container">google_updates</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">google_docs_change</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">ai_models</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">ai_overviews_llm_seo</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">technical_seo</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">content_eeat</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">tools_platforms</span>, <span class="text-primary-container">industry_news</span>.</p>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
